<p><em>"As web developers, we should choose the best tools and technology for the job. To do otherwiseâ€”out of ignorance or some duty to "web standards"â€”is a disservice to the clients and customers we serve."</em></p>
<p>Part of how we decide on the right tool is how the user experience is crafted. We do a disservice to our clients to provide them with a sub-optimal user experience for any reason that is not dictated by the target users. </p>
